        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>Richmond Va July 31<hi rend="sup">st</hi> 874<lb/></p>
                
            <p>Rev. S. Morais Pha<lb/></p>
                
            <p>My dear friend&#33;<lb/></p>
                
            <p>It was not my fault&#44; that I did not answer<lb/> your letter and did not comply with your wishes<lb/> immediately&#44; for I was absent&#44; and Mr Haser<lb/> &#40;who promised to take the book along&#41; was pre<lb/>vented to leave&#44; but is now in Pha at Mr.<lb/> Is. Cohen Girard Av. Shoe store near second st&#41;.<lb/>  I hope that you are by receiving this letter<lb/> in possession of the &#91;Hebrew&#93;.  It is the edition<lb/> of &#91;Hebrew&#93; in Berlin.<lb/></p>
            <p>I have some other books viz&#58; &#91;Hebrew&#93; <del>from</del> of<lb/> Salomo de Oliveyra.  His poetry reminds on Gabirol<lb/> &#40;see a sketch of his life in Frankels monthly<lb/> 1861. page 432.&#41; &#91;Hebrew&#93; <del></del> from&#93; of &#91;Hebrew&#93; on<lb/> the same style as Immannel &#38; Dante.<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>The second part &#91;Hebrew&#93; of Jacob Daniel<lb/> Olmo from Fisaro &#40;Metz &#91;Hebrew&#93;&#41; &#91;Hebrew&#93; of<lb/> Nerachyah Manakdan&#44; all our others are at<lb/> your disposal&#44; and am pled&#91;&#63;&#93; to <sic>assisst</sic> you.<lb/>  Your sketches are not only pleasant but instruc<lb/>tive and you deserve great praise for it.<lb/>  Please do not <sic>forgett</sic> to send me back<lb/> the &#91;Hebrew&#93; of Saadyah with the same Mr<lb/> Haser.<lb/></p>
            <p>Have you a large &#91;Hebrew&#93; &#40;Lamberg edition&#41; with all &#91;Hebrew&#93;&#63;<lb/>  I would like to exchange them for some other<lb/> valuable books<lb/></p>
            <p>To morrow please God&#44; I will preach on &#34;My<lb/> wallsâ€ž &#40;Is. 49&#44;16&#41; &#91;&#63;&#93; &#38; &#91;Hebrew&#93; of &#91;&#63;&#93;.<lb/></p>
            <p>I hope to pass through Pha. in a short<lb/> time.<lb/>
                God bless you and all of yours&#33;<lb/>
                Your friend<lb/>
                De&#91;&#63;&#93;<lb/></p>
        </body>
